title: [Sleeping Drake Harbor, Yuzu Way]
description: Silvery moonlight settles over the cobblestone street, outlining lime-washed floral designs in a gentle glow.  Lanterns sway among the apricot, carob, and tamarisk branches, their warm, golden light casting playful shadows that drift across the lane.  Deep hues cloak a bright red shop facing a three-story vivid green library, each struture decorated in shutters that are touched by the subtle silvery light.  Pampas grass near the roadside sways in the starlight, its feathery plumes resembling strands of luminous silk.
